de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Case

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Case
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, Serializable, Comparable<Object>

    public class Case
extends ErpsData
implements Comparable<Object>
    The case represents the correspondence to a common topic which is defined e.g. with the help of the subject. The case can contain one or more questions. The service center case is a from system reserved case. In that case the service center mails are located. The case is generated just once and only if the customer is created.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
    was:
    Vorgang How to use: for the client call: Case ccase = new Case(); ccase.setTitle("test"); ccase.setCustomerId(id); API.getClientAPI().getCaseAPI().store(ccase);
